Posts.Content: It's true. And I had a similar story more recently. I started to take Ostarine 4 months ago. Strange, but my nipples started to feel different and i groped for small lump under right nipple which is sore to touch. It all looked like bit painful and always itchy. I started looking answers on the internet and came across a website gynecomastiapro.com. Already there I read, that any drugs can cause gynecomastia just as much as hormone therapy.
Posts.Title: Reclinging Testosterone 18 months AFTER last Lupron? And also Multiple Kidney stones
